</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="27.[178,1085,990,1041]" pageId="27" pageNumber="1540">
E t y m o l o g y: The trivial name, 
<emphasis box="[556,620,990,1011]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="1540">versus</emphasis>
(= line), is a Latin noun. I refer to the narrow flavotestaceous line on the pronotal disc.
</paragraph>
